{"tid":939264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓女團Blackpink商業廣告太暴露 遭印尼禁播","createTime":"2018-12-13T03:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T03:41:55.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29ffc749fe5109c74001f04047d603d658844907","tid":939264,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:23:34.000Z","msg":"〔中央社〕韓國知名女團Blackpink身穿迷你裙為印尼電商Shopee宣傳的一則電視廣告，遭到印尼當局下令禁播，引起Blackpink印尼粉絲的激烈反彈。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，印尼廣播委員會（Indonesian Broadcasting Commission）昨晚以廣告不雅為由，命令國內11家電視臺停播這支廣告。<br />\n<br />\n廣告播出後，印尼廣播委員會收到超過10萬人署名請願，要求撤下廣告。不過，這也引發了一場以牙還牙的行動，撤廣告的請願發起女性面臨開除的聲浪。<br />\n<br />\n韓國知名女團Blackpink4名成員在廣告中載歌載舞，為印尼電商Shopee宣傳。印尼廣播委員會表示，這支廣告藐視全球最大穆斯林國家的道德規範。<br />\n<br />\nShopee回應表示，這是「非常寶貴的意見」；不過，公司補充說，廣告在播出之前已獲得另一個政府機關的同意。<br />\n<br />\n印尼禁播Blackpink廣告的決定，已在印尼粉絲圈招致廣泛批評。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2640932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2640932&d=jlMUGUNBB2JG8BQortsepTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f60b8b47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2640932&h=b778a682\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2640932</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a52a29ffee2875f2be6d8e76afc22dffbb09f39","tid":939264,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d239e42b72b06c61f598b6a1bd789e5c11e4eea9","tid":939264,"uid":63452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a52a29ffee2875f2be6d8e76afc22dffbb09f39","tid":939264,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fz5mVWJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%